message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present you with our premium product, which I believe would significantly benefit your endeavors. Given its exceptional value and quality, it's worth noting that the product is valued at $12000 to you. Considering this, I propose a fair offer of $11000 for the product. This price not only ensures a mutually beneficial transaction but also allows for a reasonable profit margin for me. I look forward to your positive response and the opportunity to serve you better.
